OL,3,COver half of election candidates faced
OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FWords by Political Correspondent
OL,7,FShehab Khan and Politics Producer Maya
OL,8,FBowles
OL,10,FMore than half the candidates in the
OL,11,FJuly General Election faced
OL,12,Fharassment, intimidation, or abuse,
OL,13,Faccording to a major report by the
OL,14,Felections watchdog.
OL,16,FThe findings from the Electoral
OL,17,FCommission reveal a concerning level
OL,18,Fof hostility directed at those running
OL,19,Ffor office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
