OL,3,COver half of election candidates faced
OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FReacting to the report, the
OL,7,Fgovernment's advisor on political
OL,8,Fviolence, Lord Walney, told ITV News
OL,9,Fthat without more government action to
OL,10,Ftackle threats against candidates and
OL,11,FMPs, "we risk repeats of the kind of
OL,12,Fviolent attacks which have seen
OL,13,Ffrontline politicians be murdered".
OL,15,FThe review revealed 55% of candidates
OL,16,Fencountered some form of abuse or
OL,17,Fintimidation, while 56% opted to avoid
OL,18,Fcertain campaign activities out of
OL,19,Ffear for their safety.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
