OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FChief Executive of the Electoral
OL,7,FCommission Vijay Rangarajan said the
OL,8,Flevel of harassment and intimidation
OL,9,Ffaced by candidates was "concerning"
OL,10,Fand requires "urgent and coordinated
OL,11,Faction."
OL,13,FHe warned the abuse is "deterring some
OL,14,Fpeople from standing to be candidates,
OL,15,Fand inhibiting how some engage with
OL,16,Fvoters".
