OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FPreet Gill, the Labour MP for
OL,7,FBirmingham Edgbaston, said she's no
OL,8,Fstranger to abuse, but that this
OL,9,Felection was unprecedented in terms of
OL,10,Fthe harassment she faced.
OL,12,FDuring the campaign she had to report
OL,13,Fincidents to the police four times,
OL,14,Fafter she was verbally harassed while
OL,15,Fout with her daughter, had her
OL,16,Fcampaign placards targeted by vandals,
OL,17,Fand received abuse and death threats
OL,18,Fon social media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
