OL,6,F"It's not fair game that MPs should
OL,7,Fput up with this... I want to be able
OL,8,Fto walk about freely like everybody
OL,9,Felse", she told ITV News.
OL,11,FShe revealed her teenage children have
OL,12,Fbecome aware of the kind of daily
OL,13,Fthreats she faces, adding: "They
OL,14,Flegitimately ask me, 'Is someone going
OL,15,Fto kill you?'"
OL,17,F"When my daughter said that to me, I
OL,18,Fjust burst into tears."
