OL,3,COver half of election candidates faced
OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FMany of the threats Gill faced during
OL,7,Fthis election were from people unhappy
OL,8,Fwith Labour's response to the war in
OL,9,FGaza. The words "murderer" and "blood
OL,10,Fon hands" were written on her campaign
OL,11,Fposters.
OL,13,FDiscussions about the safety of MPs'
OL,14,Fhave escalated since the October 7
OL,15,FHamas attacks in 2023 and the Israeli
OL,16,Fmilitary campaign in Gaza - with
OL,17,Fheightened tensions about the conflict
OL,18,Fspilling into the campaign trail for
OL,19,Fmany candidates in the July election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
