OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FThe Electoral Commission report
OL,7,Fhighlighted: "Ongoing international
OL,8,Ftensions in some cases led to an
OL,9,Fincrease in antisemitic and
OL,10,FIslamophobic abuse directed at
OL,11,Fcandidates."
OL,13,FThe murders of MPs Jo Cox in 2016 and
OL,14,FSir David Amess in 2021 shook
OL,15,FWestminster, sparking a whole new
OL,16,Fdebate about the safety of our elected
OL,17,Frepresentatives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
