OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FWhile the government has increased
OL,7,Fsecurity funding and support for MPs,
OL,8,Ftheir own advisor on political
OL,9,Fviolence urged them to go further.
OL,11,FLord Walney told ITV News:
OL,12,F"Unfortunately we risk repeats of the
OL,13,Fkind of violent attacks which have
OL,14,Fseen front line politicians be
OL,15,Fmurdered"
OL,17,F"But on a wider level we risk driving
OL,18,Fthe very people we need to be coming
OL,19,Finto politics... we risk those people
OL,20,Fgoing: 'I don't want anything to do
OL,21,Fwith this'".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
