OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FNigel Farage, the leader of Reform UK,
OL,7,Fhad a milkshake thrown at him during
OL,8,Fthe election campaign. And one of his
OL,9,Fparty's candidates, Steve Rubidge,
OL,10,Fsuffered "severely torn ligaments"
OL,11,Fafter an altercation while out
OL,12,Fcampaigning.
OL,14,FRubidge was handing out leaflets in
OL,15,Fthe Truro and Falmouth constituency
OL,16,Fwhen a man started verbally harassing
OL,17,Fhim and then stole his bag with
OL,18,Fcampaign materials, wallet and keys
OL,19,Finside.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
