OL,6,FMr Rubidge said he chased the man, and
OL,7,Fa physical tussle ensued as he tried
OL,8,Fto grab the bag back. He alleges the
OL,9,Fman punched and hit him.
OL,11,F"It did make me think - is this worth
OL,12,Fit?" he said.
OL,14,F"It was right at the beginning of my
OL,15,Fcampaign... you're then more wary
OL,16,Fabout how people are reacting,
OL,17,Fespecially the ones that start
OL,18,Fshouting at you in the street."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
