OL,6,FParliament welcomed a major new step
OL,7,Fin efforts to tackle the threats MPs
OL,8,Fface in October, as it agreed to set
OL,9,Fup a Speaker's Conference to look at
OL,10,Fthe issue.
OL,12,FThere have only been eight Speaker's
OL,13,FConferences in the last hundred years,
OL,14,Fusually convened to tackle issues
OL,15,Faround elections.
OL,17,FIt will consider factors influencing
OL,18,Fthe threat levels against candidates
OL,19,Fand MPs during the election period and
OL,20,Fthe effectiveness of the response to
OL,21,Fthose threats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
