OL,6,FA House of Commons spokesperson told
OL,7,FITV News that abuse and intimidation
OL,8,Fwas "completely unacceptable" and that
OL,9,Fit is "fundamental to our democracy"
OL,10,Fthat MPs and their staff are able to
OL,11,Fdo their jobs safely.
OL,13,F"As part of the comprehensive
OL,14,Finduction of MPs in the new
OL,15,FParliament, a full range of security
OL,16,Fadvice and services has been provided
OL,17,Fto new and returning Members," the
OL,18,Fspokesperson added.
